<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/674269-am-a-religious-guy-do-you-believe-that">am a religious guy, do you believe that after reading the book i will have a divorce with religion?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_674269'><a id="like_count_community_question_674269" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/674269?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F80458.The_Future_of_an_Illusion">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/674269-am-a-religious-guy-do-you-believe-that">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/674269-am-a-religious-guy-do-you-believe-that">Add your answer</a>
