<span id="freeTextContainer470313553918940311">Illusions, as referred to here, are nothing more than a person&apos;s inability to accept reality. Religion is one such illusion, but a necessary one in a time when science and its understanding by the everyday man was (and still is) at such a low point.</span>
  <span id="freeText470313553918940311" style="display:none">Illusions, as referred to here, are nothing more than a person's inability to accept reality. Religion is one such illusion, but a necessary one in a time when science and its understanding by the everyday man was (and still is) at such a low point.</span>
